{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"955494ed9e","title":"关于部队学习游泳的批示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ae76f98ed0","index":0,"year":1964,"month":8,"day":6,"articleId":"955494ed9e"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui5","name":"毛泽东思想万岁(1961-1968卷)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui5a.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui5":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"742fb068c1","type":"title","text":"关于部队学习游泳的批示","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"955494ed9e"},{"id":"2b47a9147c","type":"paragraph","text":"此件看了，很好。是否在一切有条件的地方，部队的大多数人都可以试验学游泳？军委是否已发出了指示？","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"955494ed9e"},{"id":"2e7a9adb0c","type":"paragraph","text":"条件不好，主要是：（一）有吸血虫及其他毒害的河流、池塘；（二）有大漩涡的河流地段；（三）有鲨鱼的海中。此外，部队中总有一部分不适宜于游水的，不要强令人人都下水。","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"955494ed9e"}],"page":{"id":"f9c55deffc","publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"955494ed9e","start":288,"end":288}}}},"__N_SSG":true}